    <div class="note">
      Search any world book for free. Read and translate books instantly.<br>
      <b>How it works:</b> Type your book’s name, click search, select your language, and start reading.<br>
      <span style="color:#7bb4c7">Serenity 3D UI | SathyadarshanaAI | Powered by global open libraries</span>
    </div>
